                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-32-off175 t17980110-32-cd176"></join>, a kerseymere waistcoat, value 2s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980110-32-victim343" type="victimName">
